  "title": "Part Time Office Adminstrative Executive",
  "description": "<p>Job description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Administrative duties for clients’ management. (EG. Sending letters / gifts / cards / following up on queries and requests.)</li>\n  <li>Administrative duties for organization matters. (EG. Taking minutes / managing campaigns and schedules / Filing / Scanning.)</li>\n  <li>Handling phone calls</li>\n  <li>Data-Entry in preparation of clients’ meetings and organization’s meetings</li>\n  <li>Posting advertisements, Screening candidates and scheduling Interviews.</li>\n  <li>Assisting to manage Social Media Account and content generation such as simple editing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Computer literate</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Powerpoint) and Social media</li>\n  <li>Able to do simple editing on Capcut</li>\n  <li>Fluent in English</li>\n  <li>Good attitude, Has initiative, Meticulous and a Team player</li>\n</ul>",
